- 'Most celebrated' refers to the director with the highest number of Facebook likes;
- 'Proven track record' means the director has directed more than one film;
- 'Featured an actor who has appeared in over five movies' means the film includes an actor with significant acting experience.

sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) AS num_directors_with_more_awards
FROM directors
WHERE director_awards_won > (SELECT AVG(actor_awards_won) FROM actors);

external_knowledge:
- "Shining stars in the cinematic galaxy" refers to actors who have a significant presence in the film industry;
- "Graced the screens in at least five films" means the actor has participated in at least five movies;
- "Garnered the admiration of over a thousand Facebook fans" means the actor has more than 1000 Facebook likes;
- "Honored with at least two prestigious awards" means the actor has won at least two awards.

sql:
